caption.p: Principal component analysis (Score plots) of the essential oils obtained from Angolan Lippia multiflora Moldenke. ( a) Score plot of PC1 vs. PC2; ( b) Score plots of PC2 vs. PC3; ( c) Score plots of PC1 vs. PC3. A = L1; B = L2; C = L3; D =L4; E = L5; F = L6; G = L7; H = L8a; I = L8b; J = L9a; K = L9b.
